<section class="section-padding" style="background-color: var(--color-bg);">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>{{ section.settings.title | default: 'Awareness, Built Into Your Day' }}</h2>
      <p>{{ section.settings.subtitle | default: "PostureTru won't promise an overnight transformation. It gives you a steady, gentle signal so better posture becomes a habit, not a struggle." }}</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-4">
      <!-- Benefit 1 -->
      <div class="benefit-card">
        <div class="benefit-num">01</div>
        <h3>Awareness, Not Guesswork</h3>
        <p>You stop wondering if you are slouching and start noticing the moment it happens. That small shift in awareness is where better posture starts.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Benefit 2 -->
      <div class="benefit-card">
        <div class="benefit-num">02</div>
        <h3>A Habit That Builds Itself</h3>
        <p>Each gentle vibration is a small nudge in the right direction. Over time, those nudges add up to a habit you do not have to think about anymore.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Benefit 3 -->
      <div class="benefit-card">
        <div class="benefit-num">03</div>
        <h3>Comfortable Enough to Forget</h3>
        <p>Lightweight and made from soft, food-grade silicone, PostureTru fits naturally under your clothes. Most people forget they are wearing it after the first few days.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Benefit 4 -->
      <div class="benefit-card">
        <div class="benefit-num">04</div>
        <h3>Built for Long Days</h3>
        <p>Whether you are coding, studying, or deep in a game, PostureTru works quietly through all of it. No apps to check, no routines to follow.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Product Benefits",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "title",
      "label": "Heading",
      "default": "Awareness, Built Into Your Day"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "subtitle",
      "label": "Subheading",
      "default": "PostureTru won't promise an overnight transformation. It gives you a steady, gentle signal so better posture becomes a habit, not a struggle."
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
